# RUN: midenc -Zlint -Canalyze-only %S/../../fixtures/masm/cross_module_advice_taint/miden-project.toml 2>&1 | filecheck %s

CHECK-LABEL: lib/support.masm
CHECK:  unconstrained advice data is consumed here as a constrained value

CHECK-LABEL: lib/mod.masm
CHECK: exec.support::dirty
CHECK: unconstrained value is passed as a call argument here

CHECK-LABEL: lib/mod.masm
CHECK: adv_push.1
CHECK: advice data is obtained here which is later used unconstrained
